strings.Value: "Wait a bit. I have to do something first."
{n}While you enter the capital, Regongar pulls you close and whispers,{/n} "I want you. Right now — or I'm gonna die."
"Ha ha, that would be nice. Too bad your subjects wouldn't understand."
{n}Holding you by the arm tenderly, Regongar almost runs with you to the palace.{/n}
"This is more important. Seriously — don't argue! It's the most important thing in the world."
